text: Alga () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Alginsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 295 as of 2010. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Alga, Alginsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
